snippet.title: Dixotomia - Official Gameplay Trailer | Upload VR Showcase
snippet.description: Dixotomia is a roleplaying VR shooter developed by DeepMatrix. Players will embody a SpecOps contractor in a science-fiction dystopia tasked with fighting back against vampires. Dixotomia is launching soon for SteamVR and Meta Quest.
